{"tid":797324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對食真係冇要求","createTime":"2018-08-28T12:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T03:51:55.000Z","uid":77465,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25ed54803a4a220bb8e06317d6168abc3aadb98b","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"成日都有呢啲對話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友<br />\n<br />\n情景一 <br />\n朋友：你頭先食咩<br />\n我：（一啲出晒名係劣食嘅嘢 etc.明將）<br />\n朋友：好難食喎<br />\n我：係咩<br />\n朋友：咁難食都食得晒 你食開屎㗎<br />\n我： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情景二<br />\n（叫咗同一款意粉 一到我就開始食 朋友就打陣機先食 我好快就食完）<br />\n朋友：嘩 啲意粉未熟喎 又凍又硬<br />\n我：係咩 又好似係 （我已經食晒 食嗰陣我又唔覺 但事後諗起好似真係未熟 ）<br />\n朋友：你咁都食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我叫人換碟新嘅<br />\n<br />\n情景三<br />\n同情景二差唔多<br />\n朋友 （食第一啖）：陣味咁怪嘅 好似變壞咗喎<br />\n我（食咗一大半）：吓 有壞到咩 我唔覺喎<br />\n朋友（食我嗰碟）： 咁撚臭都唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打同樣情況㗎 我真係完全唔覺得有咩問題 正常食物擺得落口 食完唔嘔 我就覺得冇問題 但成日朋友 屋企人都話我食埋啲垃圾 我都唔知畀咩反應好"},{"pid":"d152973d0ff8bdf5523f7f7fc8867db28b4e8eda","tid":797324,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用？"},{"pid":"0aefbc6bf1dd82b551ecb31dcf02efd35e2f01d8","tid":797324,"uid":47099,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"metoo<br />\n淨係識分入唔入得口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428db38984689511f7078812dc18829051d2247b","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d152973d0ff8bdf5523f7f7fc8867db28b4e8eda","tid":797324,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"新會然"},{"pid":"274f18fb762ec00f24bf74780f419a6e5e16450a","tid":797324,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"肚餓屎都好食架啦 邊有錢食宵夜啊"},{"pid":"921277ee5fa3a05340933db88128909ca1e49a39","tid":797324,"uid":185377,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"我都都係= =<br />\n明明真係沒所謂...但最後又比朋友屌毒撚唔感出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bc5a52efac849a83c3256ecba58016877e1ced","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274f18fb762ec00f24bf74780f419a6e5e16450a","tid":797324,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"肚餓屎都好食架啦 邊有錢食宵夜啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"我唔肚餓都係食咩都好食"},{"pid":"cc2890e8254054707f4d79406f19dd02326a3b6c","tid":797324,"uid":167984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"有時我同朋友一齊食同一樣嘢，朋友猛話，有陣&quot;益味&quot;，但我完全聞唔到"},{"pid":"3671bc4a85d167b2f1d4610ad8365adc4ee6743d","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc2890e8254054707f4d79406f19dd02326a3b6c","tid":797324,"uid":167984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"有時我同朋友一齊食同一樣嘢，朋友猛話，有陣&quot;益味&quot;，但我完全聞唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"同感 好佩服啲人一啖就試到有咩問題"},{"pid":"ccc74a2b26687c1f0350d9a139b6b87676aee100","tid":797324,"uid":121409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"分唔到好唔好食唔緊要，你至少都分下食唔食得呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會肚痛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea04d6f93b35c9cda375dd788bc6b536ce5a8202","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccc74a2b26687c1f0350d9a139b6b87676aee100","tid":797324,"uid":121409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"分唔到好唔好食唔緊要，你至少都分下食唔食得呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會肚痛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"所以個肚成日痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37a9c6682f164db86179250721d18e996a306dc","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003dcca8d5bbefb3e52f295e0c4c3896ecf49bcd","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca77fdd3760cde39753a1cd18ec84ad2fa6198b5","tid":797324,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"一樣,有事BBQ/打邊爐都係,見差唔多熟就照食<br />\n出邊食野就算明知污髒,都係當唔知就算<br />\n<br />\n利申成日食錯野肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c643777f793b05604788001e676b032dd5b77c","tid":797324,"uid":77465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:51:55.000Z","m